        "description": "Complete API collection for Dazo Store Management System with JWT authentication.\n\n**Quick Start:**\n1. Import this collection to Postman\n2. Set up environment variables (see Environment section below)\n3. Run \"Login - Super Admin\" to get JWT token (auto-saved)\n4. Test other endpoints\n\n**Environment Variables:**\n- `base_url`: http://127.0.0.1:8000\n- `token`: (auto-saved after login)",
        "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
    },
